        <h2>
            思维里的战争的书评 · · · · · ·
            <span class="pl">(<a href="reviews">全部 1 条</a>)</span>
        </h2>
    </header>


        


<div class="review-list">
  
  
      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="5753441">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5753441/" class="title-link">国内难得能出版这样的著作</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5753441"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/68161773/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u68161773-3.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/68161773/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">醉翁亭的酒</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2013-01-24"
      class="main-meta">2013-01-24 14:06:13</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_5753441_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  国内难得能出版这样的著作。敢想，敢写，胸怀天下之忧。  书中用非常平实的语言探讨了一些重要的军事和社会学问题。  重点探讨未来之战、战术及军事学研究之惑，探讨如何培养优秀的年轻指战员。我猜这或许和作者的军校教学背景有关。  全书文风幽默、一气呵成，一点没有官僚学...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/5753441/#comments">(1回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">0有用 / 2没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_5753441_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_5753441_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





